> > 
> > Looking at some BH traces*, it appears that what Dave hit is a truncate
> > racing with a sync...
> > 
> > truncate ...
> >   ext3_invalidate_page
> >     journal_invalidatepage
> >       journal_unmap buffer
> > 
> > going off at the same time as
> > 
> > sync ...
> >   journal_dirty_data
> >     sync_dirty_buffer
> >       submit_bh <-- finds unmapped buffer, boom.
> 
